             ZAO Alrosa, Russiaâ€™s diamond
monopoly, may buy back the gas fields it sold to units of VTB
Group last year in 2012, Alrosa said in its annual report.  
 Alrosa sold the fields for $620 million last October and
may be required to buy them back for $870 million in October
2012, the company said. Alrosa and VTB are both controlled by
the government.  
